{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bgm":"bgm24_story02","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"nameNarration":"Kagome","narration":"But now I finally know what my wish is.","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"white","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"nameNarration":"Kagome","narration":"[textBlack:It won't end in sadness or despair,@you can continue to have hope!]","narrationBg":"white","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_19332.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameNarration":"Kagome","narration":"I'm the only one who can preserve the miracle@that everyone endured suffering to weave together,@so I'll use my life to build a bridge of hope!","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"narrationEffect":"out","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_19332.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":0,"posX":-50,"posY":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Kyubey, I will become a Magical Girl."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"So please, make my wish come true!"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kyubey","textLeft":"...!!"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"I want..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameNarration":"Kagome","narration":"\"Kyubey, I want the power to make you@and your kind unable to interfere with@the Automatic Purification System forever!\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"white","chara":[{"id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"posX":0,"posY":80}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameCenter":"Kyubey","textCenter":"Your wish has been granted, Kagome Satori.","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_19332.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102000,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<I heard everything, Kagome!>","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102000,"motion":200,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"Huh?! Aru, did you just speak?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<You and I are one and the same,@so it's only natural.>"},{"chara":[{"id":102000,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Now come on, let's hurry@and save all Magical Girls!>"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102000,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"Right!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11_another/208101_aruchang.png","posX":0,"posY":-70,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"bgm":"bgm20_song10","nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Some time has passed since the@interview with Yuna Kureha...>","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<As Magical Girls continue to advance...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Kagome finally made a Magical Girl@contract,>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<and started speaking on her own@without relying on me.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<It was a definitive change in her.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<It was like that back then, too.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<When Kagome interviewed the Tokime Clan...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<She was able to have a proper conversation@all by herself.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<That was amazing, and I was happy for her,@but...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<As for me...well...you know...>"},{"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","nameNarration":"","narration":"<Tokime Clan>","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_15111.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"Umm...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(I heard that everyone was gathered here, but...)"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(There are so many people...@I wonder where they are...)"},{"nameLeft":"???","textLeft":"Hey, everyone! It's over here!"},{"nameLeft":"???","textLeft":"Please pay attention!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"Hmm?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"textClear":1},{"bgm":"bgm23_tokime02","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":100,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"This is the most cutting-edge@spot in Kamihama City, the 1090!"},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Sunao","textLeft":"Many well-known companies have tenants in this@building..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Tenant? What is a tenant...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Sunao","textLeft":"A tenant is a store that has a contract with a@commercial facility."},{"chara":[{"id":770200,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Oh, I see!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Chiharu","textLeft":"For example, high-end brands like Gucci or Chanel..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"High-end brand? What is a high-end brand...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Chiharu","textLeft":"High-end brands, um...what were they again?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Sunao","textLeft":"Why don't you try searching for the answer with@your smartphone?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"I-I see...@[chara:102601:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:102601:cheek_0][chara:102601:face_mtn_ex_001.exp3.json][chara:102601:lipSynch_1]Search, search..."},{"chara":[{"id":102601}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"Ah, well..."},{"chara":[{"id":102601}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"...High-end brands refer to companies that produce@items high in both quality and price..."},{"chara":[{"id":102601,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"That's what I'm talking about!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Oh, I see!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Sunao","textLeft":"In addition, we are currently hosting a VR event..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"VR? What is VR...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Sunao","textLeft":"Uh, VR, you see...@Virtual reality is, um..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102701},{"effect":"fadeout","id":770200}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":10200